------------------------------------------------------------
	License
------------------------------------------------------------
	
	SSI is an open source project maintained by the
	Lab for Human Centered Multimedia at the University 
	of Augsburg, Germany.
	
	Core libraries are released under LGPL (see LICENSE in core folder).
	
	By default plugins are released under GPL, but individual licences 
	may apply (see LICENSE file in plugin folder).
	
	For 3rd party dependencies see the README file and additional
	license files.
	
